        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Charitable Act</strong></p> <p>This bill allows individual taxpayers who do not otherwise itemize their tax deductions a deduction in taxable years beginning in 2023 or 2024 for charitable contributions. The deduction is limited to one-third of the standard deduction allowed to such taxpayers.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
